  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to test whether Generalized Anxiety Disorder (GAD) patients that
      participate in a Stress Reduction Intervention show a brain activation pattern (assessed by
      MRI) indicative of improved emotion regulation compared to an active control intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
